{
  "stem": "20035.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And Monday morning we left.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "We took the train.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "From the train, we went on the streetcar.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Well, by the way, at that time already, what you have to understand, that a Jew was not really welcomed anywhere.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "The system in Hungary at gymnasiums or any kind of middle school or higher school is that every student had to wear a cap.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "That cap basically totally identified who you are or not who you are, but which school you belong to.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Without that cap, you couldn't enter the school grounds.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "But that cap describes which school you belonged.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "My brother had the cap which had the fasces sign, which is similar to the-- I mean, that was the official sign of the Italian government, or the Italian Nazi party, or whatever you want to call it.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "From Mussolini and everybody down, wore it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "That was similar to the-- German [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "What's-- what's-- what's the-- cross.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "But I had to wear my high school's cap which wore-- which identified me as I am belong-- I belong to the Jewish gymnasium, the Jewish high school.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So automatically, everybody knew that I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And sometimes people were just spitting at you or calling you, right in the streetcar, all kind of names.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What-- especially that particular day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, I was-- we were holding onto each other.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we worried about only one thing, get to school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As we get off to the streetcar, Monday morning, it was early in the morning.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Our school started at eight o'clock.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Hungarian police, gendarmes, and SS guards were where we get off.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were-- our school were approximately a block and a half, two blocks apart.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we get off the same-- always on the same streetcars.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Stop.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they ask the question.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
